---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Now
description: What's current this quarter — operator and editorial both. Updated quarterly.
---
<article>
  <header>
    <p class="eyebrow">Now — as of {{ now.asOf | dateLong }}</p>
    <h1>What's current this quarter.</h1>
  </header>

  <section>
    <ul class="now-list">
      {% for item in now.items %}<li>{{ item }}</li>{% endfor %}
    </ul>
    <p class="muted">Inspired by Derek Sivers' <a href="https://nownownow.com/about">/now page</a>. Updated quarterly. Last update: {{ now.asOf | dateISO }}.</p>
  </section>
</article>
